# Contributing

Thank you for your interest in these Founder First™ playbooks.

You are welcome to fork, adapt, and use these tools in your own leadership and Kingdom-minded work. Please:
- Keep the “Build the founder. Build the future.™” spirit intact
- Retain the copyright and trademark notices
- Tag @thejosehuitron on Instagram or LinkedIn or X when you share how you’re using them

For the full proprietary Founder First Approach™ coaching or certification, connect with me directly.
